data.description: Nice home with over 2,000 sq ft offering spacious rooms up & down, with 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths and a bonus room up. There is covered parking, plus an extended driveway for plenty parking. The home has been updated with new roofing, electrical, flooring. painting, fixtures, pluming, hvac and more. All appliances are newer and can stay. This home would make a great Airbnb, it's walking distance to Elvis Presley Blvd and just minutes from the airport, downtown, shopping, schools and more..
